BEGIN_PGML
a.  Here [`3x^2-2x-85`] is called the [_]{$popup}{5}.

a.  Here [`x+5`] is called the [_]{$popup2}{5}.

a.  Did Lennie set up the problem correctly?

    [_]{$radio}{5}

a.  Now finish the long division and find the quotient and remainder (if there is one).

    [` \dfrac{3x^2-2x-85}{x+5} = `] [_]{$quot}{10}

END_PGML

